Package org.parboiled.buffers

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    InputBuffer
    Abstraction of a simple char[] buffer holding the input text to be parsed.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CharSequenceInputBuffer
    An InputBuffer over a CharSequence
    DefaultInputBuffer Deprecated
    use CharSequenceInputBuffer instead
    IndentDedentInputBuffer Deprecated
    will have no replacement; the two characters used for indent and "dedent" (respectively « and ») are of common use.
    InputBufferUtils Deprecated
    will be removed in 1.1
    MutableInputBuffer
    An InputBuffer wrapping another InputBuffer and providing for the ability to insert (and undo) characters at certain index positions.
